- Start from metadata to identify the object, its requisites, tabular sections, forms, form fields, and commands.
- Add `code` only when the question is about handlers, readers, writers, callers, or business logic.
- Distinguish UI, print, exchange, and status side effects from actual write or posting behavior.
- Use `full` only when raw source or XML is needed to complete the trace.
